This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Science sub-category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) as it deals with monitoring user activity on Google spreadsheets and studying cybercriminal behavior with regards to leaked online documents. It could also belong to the sub-category of Cybersecurity (cs.CY) for similar reasons. Additionally, it involves studying user interactions with online documents, which could fall under the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) or Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper involves analyzing data and observing patterns, which could also place it in the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
